---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Performances"
  description="Live ambient piano performances in Tampere, Finland - creating spaces for healing, reflection, and connection"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
      <div class="p-6 sm:p-8 lg:p-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white text-center mb-8">
          Live Performances
        </h1>

        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 text-center mb-12 italic">
          Ambient piano improvisation at community venues around Tampere,
          Finland
        </p>

        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert max-w-none">
          <p>
            I regularly perform ambient piano improvisation at community venues
            around Tampere, Finland. My performances focus on creating spaces
            for healing, reflection, and connection.
          </p>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
              Performance Style
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-4">My live performances feature:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>
                <strong>Ambient piano improvisation</strong> - Spontaneous, contemplative
                pieces
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Intimate settings</strong> - Small community venues
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Healing focus</strong> - Music as tool for connection and
                wellbeing
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Accessible</strong> - Free or donation-based admission
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4">
              I create music in the moment, responding to the space and the
              people present. Each performance is unique and unrepeatable.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
              Past Performances
            </h2>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">
              Regular Venues (2023-Present)
            </h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li>Teon Tupa Eldercare Center, Tampere</li>
              <li>Mummon Kammari, Tampere</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">
              Collaborative Projects
            </h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>
                Finnericans (duo performances with Sirkku) - Occasional
                collaborative performances at community events
              </li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
              Book a Performance
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Interested in ambient piano improvisation for your:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-4">
              <li>Community center or cultural space</li>
              <li>Eldercare facility or wellness center</li>
              <li>Yoga studio or meditation space</li>
              <li>Gallery or intimate venue</li>
              <li>Special event or gathering</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              <a
                href="https://freemusicarchive.org/music/Brylie_Christopher_Oxley/contact"
                class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                >Contact me</a
              > to discuss possibilities.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 italic">
              I'm particularly interested in performances that align with
              healing, community connection, and accessible culture.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
              Listen to Live Performances
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              I occasionally livestream performances and creative sessions on <a
                href="https://www.youtube.com/@brylie_music"
                target="_blank"
                class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 underline">YouTube</a
              >. These sessions offer a window into the improvisation process
              and creative work.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-4">Recent livestreams typically feature:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-4">
              <li>Piano improvisation</li>
              <li>Music production process</li>
              <li>Ambient soundscape creation</li>
              <li>Behind-the-scenes of album development</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              <a
                href="https://www.youtube.com/@brylie_music"
                target="_blank"
                class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                >Subscribe on YouTube</a
              > to get notified about upcoming livestreams.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Philosophy</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              I see live performance as community service rather than
              self-promotion. Music can create spaces for:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Reflection and contemplation</li>
              <li>Connection between people</li>
              <li>Healing and wellbeing</li>
              <li>Joy and shared experience</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4">
              My performances aim to serve these purposes, whether in eldercare
              facilities, community centers, or other intimate settings.
            </p>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
